issue.body:
Suppose I have objects like:

```
{ 
  "myList": [
      {
          "foo": "bar
      }
  ]
}
```

Doing: assertThat(list).usingFieldByFieldElementComparator().contains(item); I end up in org.assertj.core.util.Objects#areEqual which calls List.equals() and then it doesn't use field comparison anymore
